  "stemHtml": "<p>Refer to figures or AMSTERDAM - Charts 10-2, 10-2A, 10-2B, 10-2C from Jeppesen GSPRM 2017.<br>You are flying from Paris to AMSTERDAM SCHIPHOL (EHAM) but due to operational limitations, they are taking all approaches from the west. Which routes should you use?</p>",
